{"tid":1408841,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[唔係分化，唔好嘈交]係銅鑼灣嗌黃大仙嘅同我入黎","createTime":"2019-08-04T18:29:08.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-04T19:17:32.000Z","uid":149250,"like":2,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"76be3d3947e35a21ecebf90b47cd9c4ffeccd9d3","tid":1408841,"uid":149250,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T18:29:08.000Z","msg":"唔係分化，但係點解係黃大仙，晏晝已經有水馬有佈防，之後銅鑼灣叫完冇耐之後，黃大仙就已經一大堆狗，我明大家心入面都係需要一個領袖，有人決策，有人帶住會個心定好多，但係係咪真係可行，大家都要思考下係咪做到，高唔高風險，見到有post話轉場要快，前線係用緊前途幫大家爭取時間，冇錯係，但係我好怕佢地幫我地爭取嘅時間就比我地攞左黎送頭，我真係想知點解要嗌黃大仙，成架車嘅人都好疑惑，愈睇資訊又覺得奇怪同危險。我好希望係自己人做嘅，因為我地可以討論可以改變，但係唔想比人帶風向，唔想有手足有事，因為一個都不能小"},{"pid":"d27f5db6b0fad28230a3c78b7b288d7c7a4c9075","tid":1408841,"uid":149250,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T18:29:18.000Z","msg":"屌開左吹水台"},{"pid":"ee4a0fba13be53a6b7d43a531b76c335596690f1","tid":1408841,"uid":149250,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T18:29:45.000Z","msg":"推唔到有人就過返去再開"},{"pid":"37c0b251a0d4f28a06da2cddf85c1c07093605bf","tid":1408841,"uid":149250,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T18:29:57.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"dc8e94f386b40eec9bb8f5b3ee55ab63dceb1db6","tid":1408841,"uid":149250,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T18:30:20.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"63d61e3ac638d302c05d974e391f4c134cf2a612","tid":1408841,"uid":149250,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T18:30:31.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"6f277af66af93dca24a22446ea90bd5db27cda2a","tid":1408841,"uid":149250,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T18:31:07.000Z","msg":"負評講下唔該"},{"pid":"e363784eb6b6ab0a71b0c2dec7693dcc238ba5e1","tid":1408841,"uid":149250,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T18:31:24.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ea7c986de434061542b279152fb34c6d49e07131","tid":1408841,"uid":2679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T18:31:50.000Z","